column5: Has anybody ever fished gooseneck lake west of minaki on the road to whitedog #####? i will be staying in the area the last week of may and would like to know more about this lakei have heard that there are some good size nothern but would like to confirm this. also is the landing in good shape or will i have trouble landing a 17ft seanymph with a 70 hp on itthanks in advance
